abstract: The police say there is no reason to believe that the attack was related to a string of assaults in South Brooklyn that has left many residents on edge.

lead_paragraph: A 23-year-old woman fought off what the police say was an attempted sexual assault by a man in Queens on Sunday evening.

headline.main: Woman Fights Off Attacker in Queens
